ISLAMABAD, Jan 06 (APP):Special Assistant to Prime Minister on Information and Broadcasting Dr Firdous Ashiq Awan on Monday said the unified stand of all political forces on an important national issue was reflection of political maturity and strength of democracy.
In a tweet, she said that unity of political parties on the national security issue was also manifestation of keeping national security, defence and national interests supreme.
